gomodel:SYNGO_549  a      owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Immuno-EM localization of IRSp53 (BAIAP2) in the CA1 stratum radiatum of rat hippocampus. Numerous IRSp53 immunogold particles are associated with postsynaptic structures.\n\nFig. 3 Colocalization of IRSp53 with PSD-95 in cultured neurons and synaptic localization of IRSp53 in brain sections. Shows colocalization of IRSp53 and PSD-95 in cultured hippocampal neurons (21 DIV).\n\nFurthermore crude synaptosomal extracts of adult rat brain immunoprecipitated with IRSp53 shows IRSp53 interaction with PSD-95 family in brain (Fig.2).. Experimental description: Immuno-EM localization of IRSp53 (BAIAP2) in the CA1 stratum radiatum of rat hippocampus." ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
